🎨 Visual Style Direction

Keep it:
	•	minimal
	•	sharp
	•	slightly tactical / technical
	•	NOT playful Pokémon UI—more like:
	•	military briefing card
	•	trading card for systems
	•	Notion + Stripe + Palantir vibes

Color system
	•	Red: header / identity
	•	Blue: invariant (truth layer)
	•	Yellow: mechanism (action layer)
	•	Purple: use cases (application layer)
	•	Black/Grey: failure modes (risk layer)

This encodes meaning visually.

